      "title": "An auto diesel ship will arrive today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A ship carrying a load of auto diesel is scheduled to reach the island today. Accordingly, the unloading of fuel from the ship is scheduled to start from this afternoon."
